WEBVTT

1.1
00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:04.970
The customer asked: what happens after I share my layout?

1.2
00:00:04.970 --> 00:00:09.940
This module gives you the whole journey — theirs and ours.

2.1
00:00:09.940 --> 00:00:14.159
Three steps.

2.2
00:00:14.159 --> 00:00:18.378
We prepare a customised proposal and estimate from their drawings.

2.3
00:00:18.378 --> 00:00:22.597
Once the budget aligns, Sales creates the detailed technical drawings.

2.4
00:00:22.597 --> 00:00:26.816
And on confirmation, the order enters production.

3.1
00:00:26.816 --> 00:00:33.921
End to end, final order to installation runs about three to four months, depending on site conditions and design complexity.

3.2
00:00:33.921 --> 00:00:41.026
Site visits come after design discussion and commercial alignment.

3.3
00:00:41.026 --> 00:00:48.131
Samples are always available.

3.4
00:00:48.131 --> 00:00:55.236
And assembly is factory-engineered: CNC-precision panels, pre-cut, edge-finished, fixed with specialised hardware — not just adhesives.

4.1
00:00:55.236 --> 00:00:59.265
Now zoom out.

4.2
00:00:59.265 --> 00:01:03.294
The full Magppie journey runs in four phases.

4.3
00:01:03.294 --> 00:01:07.323
Phase one, sales-led acquisition — that's you, with BD.

4.4
00:01:07.323 --> 00:01:11.353
Phase two, design-led detailing.

4.5
00:01:11.353 --> 00:01:15.382
Phase three, factory-led production.

4.6
00:01:15.382 --> 00:01:19.411
Phase four, aftercare.

4.7
00:01:19.411 --> 00:01:23.440
Know what happens before and after your phase — it's how you speak about the whole company with confidence.

5.1
00:01:23.440 --> 00:01:28.596
Your process notes.

5.2
00:01:28.596 --> 00:01:33.752
One — layout, then proposal and estimate, then technical drawings, then production.

5.3
00:01:33.752 --> 00:01:38.908
Two — about three to four months from final order to installation.

5.4
00:01:38.908 --> 00:01:44.064
Three — four phases: sales-led acquisition, design-led detailing, factory-led production, aftercare.

5.5
00:01:44.064 --> 00:01:49.220
Sales owns phase one.

6.1
00:01:49.220 --> 00:01:53.986
Three steps after the layout, three to four months to installation, four phases around it all.

6.2
00:01:53.986 --> 00:01:58.752
Quiz time.

